title: Naruto x UT
synopsis: All-new animation offered throughout UNIQLO clothing stores in Japan on January 1, 2011. The DVD contains an exclusive version of Mayonaka Orchestra, by the Japanese rock band Aqua Timez. A limited number of the DVDs was offered as presents to people who bought UNIQLO's Naruto graphic T-shirts online or in their stores.
characters: ['Uzumaki, Naruto', 'Hatake, Kakashi', 'Uchiha, Sasuke', 'Haruno, Sakura', 'Uchiha, Itachi', 'Gaara', 'Pain', 'Hyuuga, Neji', 'Orochimaru', 'Tobi']
